  id: 
  displayName: Charge
  description: When an object is Shocked, it gains Charge. Certain objects will require
    Charge to activate certain abilities. Sometimes, Charge is reset to 0 after the
    object is triggered. If a Charged object is not Shocked for 2 seconds, it begins
    losing 2 Charge per second.
